Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous! Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Adventure of Little Robot Sam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cool? Super Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how lucky for him to not get hurt shooting all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Tom Stanton is so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also going to be an action hero like Stanton soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Honk, honk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You could never do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids! The draw for the set tour has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get selected, can I meet Tom Stanton?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wow, let's go! -Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Numbers 2015, 2092, 2208, 2301 have been drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-No way! -Is it yours, Uran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed it only by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let me see, I'm number 2297. -I'm 2298.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-2299. -I'm 2302.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 2301.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom, we are friends, right? -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give me that number? I can pay you as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that, I only have one winning ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you are going to give it to me, right? You are my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uran! -What a kind brother you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, an antique robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a doll. I'm for the role of robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's Tom Stanton! -It's the real Tom Stanton!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-Super Zero! -How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Only for five minutes. No autographs, and only pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push! Keep the line! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sexual harasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh, what is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for Mr. Stanton to go shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over now, over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Those in the set tour, please come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've hid well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's like a sauna. -It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who is that? -Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a surveillance. We can't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to see the real action!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike what I expected, it's messy inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We will shoot now. Ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Mr. Stunt mini robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Stanton. Please standby with the makeup for the next scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Wash and fuel this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Shall we begin then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut! Okay. It was the best acting, Stanton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we shoot the love scene with Amazones now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Zero. I can't live without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah... So there was this kind of manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that small robot earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are made well. I could never see you as a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be trapped inside here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn isn't coming back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm running out of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a robot as the same as you are. I'm Uran. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uran? -Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm Sam Stanton. Call me Sam. -You really do look alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was made to act as a double for Tom Stanton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the dangerous action scenes were done by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't do anything but he became a popular star.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... If people find out it was done by a robot, they won't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you fine with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'd like to watch the movie I'm in even if it's only for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen the movie you are in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When my turn is over, I get to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll take you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't. I will get scolded if they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who shall I date next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there was a person. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you! What are you going to do to Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An action star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Would Mr. Stanton be okay? -Leave that kind of guy alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Mr. Stanton?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been treated like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh. We got that robot stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If people find out about Sam, my popularity is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Please find him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What, it's only a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, cut! Cut! Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You can't enter the zero gravity studio on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, somebody get that kid out of here! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is this the room with no gravity? -We shoot all the space scenes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There she is. Hey! Grab her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, it's the manager. -He's on the bad side. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn off the zero gravity switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch her! She's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah, what is this? -It's a giant shark robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the next opponent I'll fight in the next Super Zero movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing... It really looks real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You got the Stanton robot stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That little girl ran away with it, thinking it's a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If the world finds out about that robot, Stanton is over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it back no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes! She wouldn't have gotten out of this studio yet, so I will for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Assign more emergency staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times did I tell you? The set tour car has gone back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But she really didn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be missing, so please let me look for her inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! I told you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All the guard robots are keeping the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something will turn out if we get to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I found her! She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come over right away! -What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice is Uran's!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let me go! -Ah, she's a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried. What trouble did you cause again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just saved this poor robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Tom Stanton!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Sam Stanton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She ran away? You stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him before the secret leaks out. If you can't bring him back, get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Sam Stanton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is an elaborate toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Dad. I told you he's the real Stanton.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Stanton a celebrity? You shouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you don't know. Let's go, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it would be better for us to move if he just think of you as a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to return him to the set after we watch the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, let's play in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We are currently looking for Sam's whereabouts with robot dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We will find the culprit by tomorrow no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him before people see him. It's confidential!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so anxious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can always make a new robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Zero series
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is popular because it is known that you act without stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right for you to get caught for lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the only things you do are shooting love scenes and holding signing events.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel angry, then try shooting at least one scene without a stuntman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, let me show you something cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's for my size.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here, this is the prince outfit. -Can I put this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to try this kind of role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a pretty princess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I can't dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-How was it? Wasn't it fun? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more fun than actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Robot dog has stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? Where is it? -This is Atom's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him back by tomorrow morning for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bye. -Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him back to the set after you watch the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Then, Sam, bye! -Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's too early to watch the movie, right? Shall we go for a walk? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe such a broad world existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a robot dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? You failed again? Stupid! -I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, call her in. I have a good thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? Don't let them be on videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been invited to the special premiere of the latest Super Zero series movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The invitation will soon be delivered. Please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's from the movie company. Sam, how great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be around here... This is next to the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This theater is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-It was built a while ago. -Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-There's no one. -I'm here to escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a weird theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran went inside with Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she didn't notice that this is a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-What a big theater. -I don't know, it's my first time being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's too dark. -Maybe the movie has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This is not a theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make both of you into scrap metal. Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran! Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go? Did she go to the movies by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from that shooting set.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they here to get Sam back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That one is a prop robot for the previous movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it doing in the theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it! Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam, you should escape here, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uran, what about you? -I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid! He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really a theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is the set I've been staying. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sam. Sam, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let Uran go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Uran?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh. We didn't do anything, but they attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They were probably trying to get rid of me before the secret gets out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dang, Atom's here. -What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet the manager here and talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom! -Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the Mega Jaws is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a sewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shark! What is it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mega Jaws for the next movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Enormous strength. All right, with my leg jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-What happened! -It has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you tried to get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-It hurts! My, it hurts... -So it was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom. -Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know all about your wicked plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought the popularity for Super Zero might go down if people find out about Sam...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, my life is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We could forgive you with certain conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-We will do anything! -Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Great Adventure of Mini-mini Prince" -Sam Stanton for the leading role
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Premiere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you the big star you already know, even though this is his debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sam Stanton!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The movie you are about to watch is a fantastic musical.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one I've always wanted to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran's idea worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A rocket escaped through buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Livian is on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Memorial circuit has been broken down due to explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Livian, for what have you come to teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Glaciers in the North Pole started melting, and there's a huge chaos in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, is this your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "Atom vs. Atlas VI"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The King in the Ice! Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "Atom vs. Atlas VI"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,fly over the sky with a jet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside my waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a machine gun's light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Searchlight's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser Blast's hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven powers, Wa Wa Wa Wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight for the peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go together
